23:26.839 --> 23:27.983
What are you talking about?

23:28.007 --> 23:29.251
You seem pretty natural with it!

23:29.275 --> 23:30.753
What?

23:30.777 --> 23:32.020
Is this something
that you guys grew up with?

23:32.044 --> 23:33.489
Did you do this when
you guys were kids?

23:33.513 --> 23:34.990
What's going on?

23:35.014 --> 23:36.525
You don't know that she's on drugs.

23:36.549 --> 23:37.460
She had one...

23:37.484 --> 23:38.393
She was on something.

23:38.417 --> 23:39.061
I know as much as you.

23:39.085 --> 23:40.463
I don't know.

23:41.854 --> 23:44.066
♪ Still wear it like a tattoo

23:44.090 --> 23:48.260
