24:08.515 --> 24:11.460
I checked her skin; She's fine.

24:11.484 --> 24:13.385
Well that's a relief.

24:16.723 --> 24:17.533
Look Jess, I'm s...

24:17.557 --> 24:18.558
I'm sorry.

24:19.692 --> 24:21.804
Come here, come here, no.

24:21.828 --> 24:23.329
Listen, I'm sorry.

24:25.665 --> 24:26.999
