was gonna put it today.

25:16.048 --> 25:16.892
I'll see you later.

25:16.916 --> 25:18.126
Bye.

25:18.150 --> 25:19.094
No no no, wait wait wait.

25:19.118 --> 25:21.220
Hailey, I made breakfast!

25:34.000 --> 25:34.834
Hi.

25:37.604 --> 25:38.413
Is this your ball?

25:38.437 --> 25:39.271
Yeah.

25:42.675 --> 25:43.485
What's your name?

25:43.509 --> 25:45.120
Penny.

25:45.144 --> 25:46.354
I'm Hailey.

25:46.378 --> 25:47.656
I like your bike.

25:47.680 --> 25:49.157
