25:58.457 --> 25:59.635
Oh.

25:59.659 --> 26:01.003
Did you meet Rachel?

26:01.027 --> 26:01.837
Rachel?

26:01.861 --> 26:02.671
My friend.

26:02.695 --> 26:04.807
She lives in your house.

26:04.831 --> 26:05.974
Oh did she move?

26:05.998 --> 26:06.833
No.

26:07.900 --> 26:09.878
Well just my family now.

26:09.902 --> 26:11.914
Rachel's there too.

26:11.938 --> 26:14.316
I haven't seen her.

26:14.340 --> 26:16.551
Doesn't mean she's not there.

26:33.860 --> 26:34.694
Yeah.

26:35.895 --> 26:37.005
Scott Green, please report

26:37.029 --> 26:38.607
to the principal's office.

26:38.631 --> 26:41.176
Scott, please report to
the principal's office.

26:41.200 --> 26:42.544
Hey.

26:42.568 --> 26:44.446
