28:49.095 --> 28:49.929
Bummer.

28:52.464 --> 28:53.299
Here.

28:56.135 --> 28:58.280
It'll be like it never happened.

28:58.304 --> 28:59.138
Okay.

29:15.721 --> 29:16.531
Hello.

29:19.391 --> 29:20.226
Hello?

29:27.133 --> 29:27.967
Hey Shae?

29:29.068 --> 29:30.278
Shae, I'm out in the garden.

29:30.302 --> 29:33.381
So if the phone rings,
could you answer it?

30:31.830 --> 30:33.075
Hey, how's it goin' over there?

30:33.099 --> 30:35.034
Hey Mike, it's goin'.

30:36.468 --> 30:37.279
Yeah?

30:37.303 --> 30:38.113
Yeah, I'm busy.

30:38.137 --> 30:39.081
You okay?

30:39.105 --> 30:40.115
You seem a little bit out of it.

30:40.139 --> 30:41.850
Long night.

30:41.874 --> 30:44.386
Actually, let me
ask you somethin'.

30:44.410 --> 30:46.688
Have you ever heard of
drain cleaner backing up

30:46.712 --> 30:48.756
and coming out of
another faucet?

30:48.780 --> 30:49.591
No.

30:49.615 --> 30:50.558
Sounds crazy right?

30:50.582 --> 30:51.726
Technically impossible.

30:51.750 --> 30:53.761
That's what I said.

30:53.785 --> 30:54.853
Why?

30:58.757 --> 31:01.603
My sister Shae was
taking a bath last night

31:01.627 --> 31:03.705
and had this freak out episode.

31:03.729 --> 31:06.508
And now my wife is convinced
that the drain cleaner

31:06.532 --> 31:10.913
I poured into our sink somehow
came up through the tub.

31:10.937 --> 31:12.380
Wait, Shae Jacobson?

31:12.404 --> 31:13.215
Yeah.

31:13.239 --> 31:14.149
That's your sister?

31:14.173 --> 31:15.083
Yeah.

31:15.107 --> 31:16.651
Wow, I used to date Shae

31:16.675 --> 31:18.520
back in college for
about two years.

31:18.544 --> 31:19.621
Oh shit.

31:19.645 --> 31:21.423
You're that Mike!

31:21.447 --> 31:23.926
Yeah, you must be Toddy Bear?

31:23.950 --> 31:25.593
Toddy Bear.

31:25.617 --> 31:27.162
Man I haven't heard
from Shae in years.

31:27.186 --> 31:28.897
How did you guys
end up over here?

31:28.921 --> 31:30.899
Well she was up here
for a while actually,

31:30.923 --> 31:32.734
takin' care of our mom.

31:32.758 --> 31:35.003
And she passed, and at
the time it made sense

31:35.027 --> 31:37.305
for my family and her
to all move in together.

31:37.329 --> 31:38.440
And she actually
found a great house

31:38.464 --> 31:39.274
in the neighborhood.

31:39.298 --> 31:40.508
Where?

31:40.532 --> 31:44.112
Amity Way, at the
end of the cul-de-sac.

31:44.136 --> 31:47.906
So how did you guys
come across that place?

31:50.042 --> 31:51.519
She answered an ad.

31:51.543 --> 31:52.854
Shae is doing all right?

31:52.878 --> 31:54.389
Yeah, no she's fine.

31:54.413 --> 31:55.223
She's a tough cookie.

31:55.247 --> 31:56.758
So she bounced back.

31:56.782 --> 31:58.293
Look, I gotta go.

31:58.317 --> 32:00.362
I might drop by later
on to say hi to Shae.

32:00.386 --> 32:02.821
Okay, yeah sounds good man.

32:11.430 --> 32:13.708
Hey, I did the inventory,
and loaded the beers.

32:13.732 --> 32:14.676
Can I go meet the guys?

32:14.700 --> 32:15.877
Storage unit locked up?

32:15.901 --> 32:16.735
Yeah.

32:18.904 --> 32:21.316
Hey, Dad if you
need me to stay...

32:21.340 --> 32:23.618
No it's all right, I got
Jones comin' in at eight.

32:23.642 --> 32:25.811
You go on, get outta here.

32:29.048 --> 32:29.857
I'll be back later.

32:29.881 --> 32:31.459
How much later?

32:31.483 --> 32:32.651
Be home by 10.

32:33.652 --> 32:34.596
No excuses.

32:34.620 --> 32:35.454
Yes sir.

32:40.659 --> 32:41.493
Hey.

32:42.394 --> 32:43.229
Hey.

32:44.963 --> 32:46.674
I was just gonna
return your jacket.

32:46.698 --> 32:48.300
Right, thank you.

32:49.801 --> 32:52.647
How did you know I was here?

32:52.671 --> 32:55.917
You said you worked
at your dad's bar.

32:55.941 --> 32:56.884
There's only two in town.

32:56.908 --> 32:57.919
And one of them's a strip club.

32:57.943 --> 32:58.953
So I used my instincts.

32:58.977 --> 33:00.179
Right, right.

33:01.747 --> 33:05.793
Well I was jut about
to get outta here.

33:05.817 --> 33:07.729
You want a ride?

33:07.753 --> 33:08.920
Um, why not?

33:14.393 --> 33:15.661
Well come on.

33:44.990 --> 33:46.368
Woo!

33:46.392 --> 33:47.826
That was awesome.

33:48.794 --> 33:49.628
Oh man.

33:51.497 --> 33:52.331
Whew.

33:55.634 --> 33:59.347
So uh, you gonna tell
me why you feel the need

33:59.371 --> 34:00.548
to carry that thing around?

34:00.572 --> 34:01.716
My crossbow?

34:01.740 --> 34:03.151
Yeah.

34:03.175 --> 34:06.621
I mean, this is a
pretty safe neighborhood.

34:06.645 --> 34:08.223
You can never be too careful.

34:08.246 --> 34:09.791
It's a historical
fact that small towns

34:09.815 --> 34:12.494
are breeding ground
for serial killers.

34:12.518 --> 34:14.753
Wow, who said that again?

34:16.054 --> 34:17.165
History.

34:17.188 --> 34:18.790
Right, of course.

34:19.690 --> 34:21.869
You ever heard of a gun?

34:21.893 --> 34:23.395
Too predictable.

34:27.833 --> 34:29.000
You wanna try?

34:30.902 --> 34:32.170
No, I'm good.

34:34.840 --> 34:39.020
You ever actually shoot
anybody with that thing?

34:39.043 --> 34:40.922
No, but I wouldn't
mind putting an arrow

34:40.946 --> 34:43.458
through my aunt Shae's ass.

34:43.482 --> 34:46.928
Okay, so you don't
like her obviously.

34:46.952 --> 34:49.955
Nope, now I have
to live with her.

34:50.989 --> 34:52.056
That sucks.

34:53.091 --> 34:54.668
Yeah.

34:54.693 --> 34:57.272
She's gone absolutely crazy.

34:57.296 --> 34:58.940
She was in the
bathtub last night.

34:58.964 --> 35:01.343
She started screaming,
crying, the whole nine yards.

35:01.367 --> 35:03.645
She thought her sin
was burning off.

35:03.669 --> 35:04.946
Burning off?

35:04.970 --> 35:08.140
Yeah like acid
burning her skin off.

35:10.642 --> 35:11.853
What?

35:11.877 --> 35:13.988
Nothing, nothing.

35:14.012 --> 35:18.493
Anyway, she went crazy and
it made my parents fight.

35:18.517 --> 35:19.827
And so they got in to
this huge argument.

35:19.851 --> 35:22.087
And it was, seriously what?

35:25.591 --> 35:27.869
I shouldn't say anything.

35:27.893 --> 35:28.727
Okay.

35:29.795 --> 35:32.898
Something bad
happened in that house.

35:34.466 --> 35:35.843
What happened?

35:35.867 --> 35:39.647
