35:47.179 --> 35:48.013
Shit.

35:48.914 --> 35:50.982
It was a long time ago.

35:52.083 --> 35:53.561
Nobody even really
talks about it anymore.

35:53.585 --> 35:56.398
That's totally creepy.

35:56.422 --> 35:59.000
Won't be taking a
bath any time soon.

35:59.024 --> 36:00.235
I'm sorry, I shouldn't
have said anything.

36:00.259 --> 36:02.661
No no no, I'm glad you did.

36:04.062 --> 36:07.566
It's nice to just have
someone to talk to.

36:12.471 --> 36:15.073
We should probably get going.

36:18.244 --> 36:19.077
Okay.

36:35.694 --> 36:37.429
Hello, hello, Shae?

36:44.035 --> 36:45.847
Yeah
boy, did you find a chicken?

36:45.871 --> 36:46.705
Hello?

36:48.106 --> 36:48.940
Hello.

36:53.144 --> 36:54.121
Shae?

36:54.145 --> 36:55.457
Shae, it's me Mike.

36:55.481 --> 36:57.549
Open up, we need to talk.

37:02.288 --> 37:03.130
Shae?

37:03.154 --> 37:04.990
Shae open up, it's me.

37:19.638 --> 37:21.949
Hey, where's Delilah?

37:21.973 --> 37:24.118
Screwin' around in the kitchen.

37:28.947 --> 37:30.525
Delilah.

37:30.549 --> 37:31.559
Mike.

37:31.583 --> 37:33.084
We have to talk.

37:34.119 --> 37:35.297
Don't stop.

37:35.321 --> 37:36.898
The people you moved
into Amity house,

37:36.922 --> 37:38.433
Shae is a good friend of mine.

37:38.457 --> 37:40.468
Shae I love her.

37:40.492 --> 37:41.903
She's an artist.

37:41.927 --> 37:44.839
Look, you have to
get them out of there.

37:44.863 --> 37:45.673
Stop.

37:45.697 --> 37:46.532
Just stop.

37:57.676 --> 38:00.221
I don't tell you how
to run your business.

38:00.245 --> 38:02.624
Don't tell me how to run mine.

38:02.648 --> 38:04.559
It's not right.

38:04.583 --> 38:06.193
You know it.

38:06.217 --> 38:09.130
Well the house can't be empty.

38:09.154 --> 38:11.666
As long as tenants pay, I
don't care who they are.

38:11.690 --> 38:13.525
You're a sick bitch.

38:16.595 --> 38:19.765
