38:27.606 --> 38:29.941
Never bet against the house.

38:47.659 --> 38:48.494
Shae?

38:54.032 --> 38:57.436
Shae, Jess is makin'
dinner I just, whoa.

38:58.704 --> 38:59.614
I'm sorry.

38:59.638 --> 39:02.040
